raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Baaaabe
Mabel: I missed youuu
Mabel: I had so much work to do 🥺
Mabel: img: mabel/80
- Missed you too!
	Player: Missed you too!
	Mabel: Mwah! 😚
- Did you forget about me?
	Player: Did you forget about me?
	Mabel: Nooo never!!
Mabel: I was seriously thinking about the club situation
if Story.has_flag(\"NTR\"):
	Mabel: Did you figure it out??
	Player: Yeah me and my friend joined the frat house! 😁
	Mabel: The frat house!? 
	Mabel: img: mabel/81
	Mabel: Yay! 🥳
	Mabel: ...
	Mabel: What's that...!? 🤣
	Player: It's supposed to be the boys club version of your club!
	Mabel: So we're not gonna be too far from each other??
	Mabel: That's definitely worth celebrating 🥳🥳
	Player: It is!
	Mabel: So glad for you babe! 🥰
	Mabel: All this club business is kinda exciting
	Mabel: I wonder what sort of activities we're gonna do 🤔
	Mabel: Do you think the girls will wanna go for a picnic?
	Mabel: That's what me and my friends from high school would do in our girl's club 😝
	Player: Hopefully you'll make more friends!
	Mabel: I'll make all the friends and be the most popular 👸
	Mabel: Alright babe
	Mabel: I'm gonna try to do some of my homework early
	Mabel: And see what this club business is about tomorrow 😁
	Player: Same!
	Player: Good luck!
	Mabel: Thanks, I'll need it
	Mabel: And you too!
	Mabel: 🥰
	Player: 😊
	Mabel: Gn babe 🩷
	Player: Gn!
	do social_post(\"caleb_naomi_overworked\")
else:
	Mabel: And that we're gonna be in the same club omg! 🥳
	Mabel: Isn't that exciting?
	do social_post(\"caleb_photoshoot\")
	Mabel: I can drag you on more dates hehe 🤭
	Player: Is that your first thought? 😆
	Mabel: Of course it is
	Mabel: It's also my second thought, and my third 😌
	Player: Wow
	Mabel: Naomi is so adorable!
	if Story.has_flag(\"LUST\"):
		Mabel: And Caleb is.. nice 🫣
		Player: 🤣
	Mabel: It'll be so much fun
	Mabel: I'm sure it will 🥰
	Player: I'm sure too
	Mabel: ...
	Mabel: PinkThought: Gee this is the perfect moment
	Mabel: PinkThought: If I don't do it now then I never can
	Mabel: Uhm... babe?
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: This is gonna sound a little strange but 😊
	Mabel: PinkThought: I totally can't do this
	Mabel: PinkThought: Pull yourself together Mabes, you can do it!!
	Mabel: Can I...
	Mabel: Maybe show you me a little...?
	Mabel: I mean girls kinda do stuff with their boyfriends right? 👉👈
	Mabel: Like sometimes they get all close and sometimes a little touchy and they like show each other stuff and... you know how it is
	Player: Mabel. What's going on? 😆
	do heart(2)
	Mabel: I just, you know how...
	Mabel: You're my boyfriend and all right?
	Mabel: And that's there's stuff that girls sometimes do with their boyfriends
	Mabel: I want to do that kind of stuff with you
	Mabel: Just some of it for now but... maybe...
	Mabel: I mean I've been meaning to... or trying to show you but maybe it's best to just talk about it
	Player: Mabel
	Player: I want to see you
	do heart(3)
	Mabel: Ok.
	Mabel: img: mabel/82
	Mabel: PinkThought: He's looking, he's definitely looking
	Mabel: PinkThought: My heart is gonna explode
	Mabel: Am I...
	Mabel: I mean d-do you like... my
	Mabel: My body?
	Player: Yeah.
	- You're beautiful
		Player: You're beautiful
	- You're hot
		Player: You're hot
	Mabel: Thanks.
	Mabel: I wanted you to know that
	Mabel: If you ever wanted more like this, you can ask me
	Mabel: I want to make you happy
	Player: You do make me happy
	Mabel: 🙈
	Mabel: Sorry for being so awkward
	do heart(2)
	- I like that about you
		Player: I like that about you
		Mabel: Gee you're so weird 🥰
		Mabel: Liking awkward me
	- You're not awkward
		Player: You're not awkward
		Player: You're perfect
	Mabel: PinkThought: Oh my god, I finally did it...
	Mabel: PinkThought: EEK!
	Mabel: Okay I'm gonna run away now to sleep before my heart explodes 🫠
	do heart(0)
	Mabel: Good night 👀
	Player: Good night ❤️
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
